                <p class="lead larger text-center"><span class="dropcap color-dark font-weight-normal">M</span>artin has a great passion for photography since 2017, he hasn't been published in any media or magazine yet but that doesn't mean he lacks the quality of his work. He also doesn't have any awards, nor he can label himself as a professional. He just loves photography for the sake of it and also escape from depression sometimes. He shoots mainly Portraits but is willing to experiment with whatever genre and is based in Sofia, Bulgaria but that can't stop him from exploring new horizons, if you need him somewhere else on the planet Earth just ask and you shall receive.</p>
